text: Beril Böcekler (born 7 February 2004, Ankara) is a Turkish swimmer. Böcekler represented Turkey at the 2018 European Juvenile Swimming Competition, 2018 Mediterranean Olympic Games and the 2020 Summer Olympics. Böcekler has the Turkish records in 400, 800 and 1500 m free-style. == References == ==Other websites== *Profile of Beril Böcekler at the Turkish Olympic Committee Category:2004 births Category:Sportspeople from Ankara Category:Swimmers Category:Sportswomen Category:Olympians for Turkey
